apihelp-donate-description: Iste API permitte submitter un donation al Fundation Wikimedia per varie methodos de pagamento.
apihelp-donate-summary: Iste API permitte submitter un donation al Fundation Wikimedia per varie methodos de pagamento.
apihelp-donate-param-gateway: Le passarella de pagamento a usar: adyen, globalcollect, etc.
apihelp-donate-param-contact_hash: Hash del donator in CiviCRM, usate pro verification. Obligatori quando contact_id es date.
apihelp-donate-param-processor_form: Qual optiones del formulario del processator usar.
apihelp-donate-param-order_id: ID del ordine (si un donation ha jam essite initiate).
apihelp-donate-param-recurring: Indica que le transaction debe repeter se periodicamente.
apihelp-donate-param-variant: Indica qual variante del formulario le donator ha reimplite.
apihelp-donate-param-opt_in: Indica que le donator ha optate pro reciper e-mails de collecta de fundos.
apihelp-logPaymentsFormError-description: Iste API registra le errores del formulario de donation al latere del cliente.
apihelp-logPaymentsFormError-summary: Iste API registra le errores del formulario de donation al latere del cliente.
apihelp-logPaymentsFormError-param-file: File in le qual le error ha occurrite
apihelp-logPaymentsFormError-param-line: Linea in le qual le error ha occurrite
apihelp-logPaymentsFormError-param-col: Columna in le qual le error ha occurrite
apihelp-logPaymentsFormError-param-stack: Tracia de pila del error, si disponibile
apihelp-di_recurring_convert-summary: Iste API es usate quando un donator accepta de adder un donation mensual post haber correctemente concludite un donation singule.
apihelp-di_recurring_convert-param-gatew: Le passarella de pagamento a usar: adyen, globalcollect, etc.
apihelp-employerSearch-description: Iste API permitte cercar empleatores que participa in le programma de donationes de contrapartita de WMF.
apihelp-employerSearch-summary: Iste API permitte cercar empleatores que participa in le programma de donationes de contrapartita de WMF.
